<h3 id="squad-depth">Squad Depth</h3>

<p>In addition to Current Squad Depth, it would also be useful to have:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Conceptual Depth (user can add shortlisted players in to see where they would fit into their squad)</li>
  <li>Future Depth (including youth players, contract expiry and future transfers)</li>
</ul>

